---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="¡Gracias por Suscribirte! | AdriCris Rueda"
  description="Gracias por unirte a la comunidad Vida Consciente. Descarga tu PDF 30 Tips de Vida."
  noindex={true}
>
  <section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-primary via-primary/95 to-accent/80 relative overflow-hidden pt-24">
    <!-- Decoraciones de fondo -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-secondary/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-80 h-80 bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center">
      <!-- Icono de éxito -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto animate-bounce">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-primary">check</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white mb-6">
        ¡Bienvenida a la<br/><span class="text-secondary italic">tribu!</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 font-light mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Tu suscripción ha sido confirmada. Revisa tu correo electrónico para más detalles.
      </p>
      
      <!-- Card del PDF -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/20 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary">redeem</span>
          <span class="text-secondary font-bold text-lg">TU REGALO DE BIENVENIDA</span>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-4">30 Tips de Vida</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Un PDF exclusivo con consejos prácticos para vivir con mayor consciencia, presencia y propósito.
        </p>
        
        <a 
          href="/downloads/30-tips-vida.pdf" 
          download
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-secondary text-primary font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-white transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg shadow-secondary/30"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">download</span>
          DESCARGAR MI PDF
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Botones adicionales -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span>
          Volver al inicio
        </a>
        <span class="hidden sm:inline text-white/40">|</span>
        <a href="https://wa.me/573132979675" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80 hover:text-secondary transition-colors">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">chat</span>
          Escribir por WhatsApp
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
